profile: Columbia Environmental is a environmental engineering firm located in Penticton offering a wide variety of services including Environmental Site Assessments, Asbestos Hazard Assessments, Contamination Remediation Services, and Biological Services. Our firm provides consulting services in both the private and public sectors including customers in land development and real estate throughout Western and Northern Canada.
